  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dc4 \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0daf\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd4. 1000\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A liter of petrol made from turmeric powder costs Rs. 1000 sold",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "On 12th, Dambulla police arrested a person on suspicion of selling five liters of turmeric powder and water for 5000 rupees, saying it was petrol.",
        "This person has been arrested based on information received by the Dambulla police, the police say that the arrested person is from the Dambulla area.",
        "A person in Dambulla area went on a bicycle to meet the young man and went to get 5 liters of petrol based on information that a certain young man was selling petrol at one thousand rupees per litre. The buyer left in a deserted place for a few minutes and took the amount of 5000 rupees and left.",
        "Later, the suspect who is in custody mixed water with yellow powder and turned it into petrol color, took the five liter can and kept it near the buyer and instructed him to leave the place immediately because the petrol marketing incident has already been reported to the police.",
        "Suspicious of the suspect running away, the buyer opened the lid and found it to be a mixture of water and yellow powder.",
        "After he immediately complained to the Dambulla Police, a police team of the Dambulla Police immediately went to the area and arrested the suspect.",
        "The police say that during the questioning of the suspect, they were able to uncover the information that he had cheated people and sold water, yellow powder and petrol in this way.",
        "Dambulla Police say that the arrested suspect is scheduled to be produced before the Dambulla Magistrate's Court."
      ],
